<div id="pf665" class="pf w22 h152" data-page-no="665"><div class="pc pc665 w22 h152"><div class="t m2768 x64 hef yc7d ff1 fs1b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One </div><div class="t m13e3 x64 hef y1c1a ff1 fs1b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sixtrfourth </div><div class="t m9a4 x5b h28 y934 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the entire wealth </div><div class="t mef x5b h28 y110b ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the United States </div><div class="t m592 x5b h28 y1078 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was absorbed by </div><div class="t m2527 x4a h28 y14f8 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">f </div><div class="t m5 x14 h28 y14f8 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">î˜‰</div><div class="t m149d x5b h28 y1079 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Trusts in 1898 a-</div><div class="t ma32 x5b h28 y1c34 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lone. </div><div class="t m2464 x8f h5f y1f96 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">During the first 15 days in December, 189E, Chicago Station Houses sheltered </div><div class="t m2769 x5c h5f y111d ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">642 homeless men. For the same time in 1896, 15,521 were thus sheltered; while </div><div class="t ma5a x5c h5f y12af ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for that time in 1897, the number was only limited by the capacity of the houses. </div><div class="t m1088 x4e h2b y1c51 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is such conditions as the above upon which our new book, </div><div class="t m5a7 x113 hcc y1c51 ff9 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&amp;raids of </div><div class="t ma69 x114 h4b y1c51 ff7 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">frye </div><div class="t m432 x115 hcc yc0f ff9 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">morning, </div><div class="t mb29 x18 h2b y1dd1 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">treats; not that it is entirely devoted to the social question, however, but that it is entirely devoted to the </div><div class="t mbfd x18 h2b y1376 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">signs of our times, of which that perplexing question is a part. Farther than that, it introduces only </div><div class="t m4b9 x18 h2b y1064 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">such signs as are of common occurrence, and which may be observed by every one. It is therefore a </div><div class="t m174e x4a h2b y2066 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book of general interest. The engravings are very fine; in fact they really illustrate the book. It will </div><div class="t m1575 x4a h2b y11cb ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">probably be the easiest selling subscription book of the year. </div><div class="t m1575 x4e h2b yf0e ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Address your State Tract Society for outfit and terms. </div><div class="t m5d1 x6d h4e y20ed ff9 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Pacific Press Publishing Co., Publishers, Oakland, </div><div class="t m20dd x116 hcc y1d41 ff9 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cal. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
